Package Logic

Class Member

java.lang.Object
Logic.Member
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
PolytechnicStaff, PolytechnicStudent
public class Member extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a member of an organization or group. This class stores member information such as first name, last name, address, phone, gender, and birth date. It also keeps track of the total number of members.

  • Constructor Details

    • Member

      public Member(String firstName, String lastName, String address, String phone, String gender, String birthDate)
      Constructor with parameters. Creates a new Member object with the provided first name, last name, address, phone, gender, and birth date. Assigns the next available ID to the new member. Increments the total number of members.
      Parameters:
      firstName - the first name of the member
      lastName - the last name of the member
      address - the address of the member
      phone - the phone number of the member
      gender - the gender of the member
      birthDate - the birth date of the member
